Title: Work Order: Fuel
Description:
Our fuel supplies are running low. Without fuel we won't be able to operate the machinery that's building this place. They might even expect me to start helping them build!

I was not built for manual labor! See these nails?! I just had them done!

Get down to the refinery and get this fuel order filled! Hurry! They were fitting me for a tool-belt this morning. It didn't even match my outfit!
ObjectivesText: Find Grizzle Gearslip in Bilgewater Beach.
